仕皮带？官方回应：系 140 元的仿制品"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-956a4a2da85e9965ba628c6542fbe0c2_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "96 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/492233148"}}, "attached_info": "ClQIhZak9pzmoqVpEAMaCDcxNjY2NTA4IKa/m4sGMAA4L0Aqcgk0OTIyMzMxNDh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "43_1634195268.998282", "card_id": "Q_491898880", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 25}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价 DC 漫画中超人的儿子小乔纳森·肯特出柜？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-68b8ed4fc59d0ef4ced1512d8319fdc0_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "93 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/491898880"}}, "attached_info": "ClQIhZak9pzmoqVpEAMaCDcxNTkyNTQ4IM/dk4sGMAM4KkArcgk0OTE4OTg4ODB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "44_1634195268.9987564", "card_id": "Q_372740215", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 78}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "压垮抑郁症患者的最后一根稻草会是什么?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我想知道抑郁症患者为什么自杀，让他自杀的那个点究竟是什么？ ——— 此问题已被收录至知乎吾辈问答第 17 期专题《心理健康，我们忽视了多少？》"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-288c84ed6a885adc4b2ab3fc2d80fab5_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "89 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/372740215"}, "text_tag_area": {"text": "吾辈问答", "font_color": "GYL01A", "background": "GYL01A"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IhZak9pzmoqVpEAMaCDQ1MTA4OTA0IKrbrfIFMAI40gJALHIJMzcyNzQwMjE1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "45_1634195268.9994457", 